# AI Aliens - Weekly Content Schedule

## Overview

Each location runs for **1 week** (Sunday to Friday), with Saturday off. New location starts every Sunday.

**Annual capacity:** 52 locations/year

---

## Weekly Schedule

| Day | Content | Time | Platforms | Workflow |
|-----|---------|------|-----------|----------|
| **Sun** | Intro Video | 8pm | Instagram, TikTok, YouTube | AI Aliens - Intro |
| **Mon** | Photos 1-5 | 5pm | Instagram (carousel + stories), TikTok, YouTube (slideshow) | AI Aliens - Snapshots |
| **Tue** | Dad Joke 1 | 5pm | Instagram, TikTok, YouTube | AI Aliens - Dad Jokes |
| **Wed** | Photos 6-10 | 5pm | Instagram (carousel + stories), TikTok, YouTube (slideshow) | AI Aliens - Snapshots |
| **Thu** | Dad Joke 2 | 5pm | Instagram, TikTok, YouTube | AI Aliens - Dad Jokes |
| **Fri** | Review Video | 5pm | Instagram, TikTok, YouTube | AI Aliens - Review |
| **Sat** | â€” | â€” | â€” | â€” |

