## Content Per Location

| Content Type | Count | Notes |
|--------------|-------|-------|
| Intro Video | 1 | Landing zone spot |
| Photo Carousels | 2 | 5 photos each (4 generic + 1 food per carousel) |
| Dad Jokes | 2 | Pulled from global jokes pool |
| Review Video | 1 | Generic spot |

---

## Spots Required Per Location

| Spot Type | Count | Used By |
|-----------|-------|---------|
| landing_zone | 1 | Intro |
| food_vendor | 2 | Snapshots (1 Mon, 1 Wed) |
| generic | 12 | Dad Jokes (2) + Snapshots (8) + Review (1) + buffer |

**Total: 15 spots per location**

---

## Other Requirements Per Location

| Tab | Count | Notes |
|-----|-------|-------|
| Foods | 2 | 1 per snapshot day |
| Dialogue | 1 row | Intro + Review dialogue |

